00:25:07.273 --> 00:25:12.329
♪Ngunit lumalabas ang mas malalim na sakit♪

00:25:13.413 --> 00:25:17.097
♪Blurring poot at pagmamahal♪

00:25:18.665 --> 00:25:23.753
♪Dapat ako ang naging fatal blade♪

00:25:24.969 --> 00:25:28.553
♪Pagputol ng mga maling akala at pagkahumaling♪

00:25:29.833 --> 00:25:41.225
♪Ngunit hindi sinasadya,
